<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3738522>
    dc:description "Figs 60-68: Meotica ochsi (60-64; 60: lectotype; 63: paralectotype; 61-62, 64: Provence) and M. smetanai (65-68): (60-62, 65-66) median lobe of aedeagus in lateral and in ventral view; (63-64, 68) spermatheca; (67) female sternite VIII. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3738522/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3738524>
    dc:description "Figs 69-79: Meotica andujari (69-73), M. ochsi (74-75), M. wunderlei (76-77), and M. normandi (78-79): (69, 74, 76, 78) male sternite VIII; (70) median lobe of aedeagus in lateral view; (71) apical portion of median lobe in ventral view; (72, 75, 77, 79) female sternite VIII; (73) spermatheca. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3738524/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

